-economy/article/3254964/chinas-inner-mongolia-seeks-avoid-economic-security-impact-hollowing-out-amid-population-pressure?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国北部的内蒙古自治区与俄罗斯和蒙古接壤，该地区对年轻人外流影响经济发展和国家安全的所谓空心化感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254964/chinas-inner-mongolia-seeks-avoid-economic-security-impact-hollowing-out-amid-population-pressure?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>